<P>
CBS breathed a sigh of relief Thursday and reported that its highest-rated 
entertainment series, "Murder, She Wrote," will return next fall for a sixth 
season. The network, running third in the prime-time ratings, already had 
locked up the professional services of the show's star, Angela Lansbury, but 
