INSURANCE INDUSTRY -- CALIFORNIA; PROPOSITION 103 (STATE INSURANCE 
COMMISSIONER); COASTAL INSURANCE CO; ROBERTI, DAVID A; GILLESPIE, ROXANI; GEICO 
CORP 
